		<div class="inner_mid_content_pane2">
		<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
  <tr>
    <td width="200" align="left" valign="top" style="border-right:solid 1px #EBEBEB">
	<div class="inner_head">Business Development</div>
	
	</td>
    <td align="left" valign="top">
	<div class="inner_content">
	 <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
       <tr>
         <td align="right"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
           <tr>
             <td width="22" align="left" valign="middle"><img src="images/print.png" width="16" height="16" /></td>
             <td align="right" valign="middle"><a href="javascript:window.print()" class="eauction-links">Print this page</a></td>
           </tr>
         </table></td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td>&nbsp;</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td><p align=justify>The Singareni Collieries Company Ltd. is the oldest Govt. Mining Company in the country having a history of more than 125 years in coal mining. The company produced 62.01 MT of coal in the year 2017-18 and is a profit making and dividend paying company. The company is strong in Modern Coal Mining Technologies in Opencast and Underground Mines, usage of IT, Equipment Maintenance, Coal Handling and Modern Management practices including implementation of Enterprise Resource Planning(ERP) project.</p></td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td>&nbsp;</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td>It has charted out an aggressive growth strategy by leveraging its core competency in Coal Mining operations by extension of its business operations into.</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td>&nbsp;</td>
       </tr>
       <tr>
         <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
